<text evidence="30">(Microbial infection) Interacts with human coronavirus NL63 spike protein.</text>
</comment>
<comment type="subunit">
<text evidence="22">(Microbial infection) Interacts with human coronavirus NL63/HCoV-NL63 spike glycoprotein.</text>
